        class="justify-center"
        format="svg"
        width={50}
        height={50}
        src="/Doodles/html_logo.svg"
        alt="Programming Language Logo"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <Image
        class="justify-center"
        format="svg"
        width={50}
        height={50}
        src="/Doodles/css_logo.svg"
        alt="Programming Language Logo"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <Image
        class="justify-center"
        format="svg"
        width={50}
        height={50}
        src="/Doodles/js_logo.svg"
        alt="Programming Language Logo"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <Image
        class="justify-center"
        format="svg"
        width={50}
        height={50}
        src="/Doodles/react_logo.svg"
        alt="Programming Language Framework Logo"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <Image
        class="justify-center"
        format="svg"
        width={50}
        height={50}
        src="/Doodles/cpp_logo.svg"
        alt="Programming Language Logo"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <Image
      class="justify-center"
      format="svg"
      width={50}
      height={50}
      src="/Doodles/go_logo.svg"
      alt="Programming Language Logo"
      loading="eager"
    />
      <Image
        class="justify-center"
        format="svg"
        width={50}
        height={50}
        src="/Doodles/node_logo.svg"
        alt="Programming Language Logo"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <Image
        class="justify-center"
        format="svg"
        width={50}
        height={50}
        src="/Doodles/git_logo.svg"
        alt="Working Tool Logo"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        I am a <b>passionate</b> student who seeks to learn something new every day,
        a <b>proficient leader</b> and a <b>self-taught</b> developer dedicated to
        deliver my services in the best way. I am looking for the opportunity to
        face new exciting challenges and <b>develop solutions</b> through collaborative
        work at the enterprise level.
        <br /><br />
        I am immersed in the programming world since <b>2020</b>, and since
        then, I have learned to handle both development and collaborative tools.
        Among the development languages that I handle are <b>JavaScript</b>, <b
          >ReactJS</b
        >, <b>SQL</b>, <b>NodeJS</b>, <b>Go</b>, etc.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
      <a
        class="btn"
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tatonaranjo/"
        target="_blank"
      >
        Let's connect!</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2 flex gap-3 items-center">
      <Image
      class="justify-center"
      format="svg"
      width={50}
      height={50}
      src="/Doodles/projects1.svg"
      alt="A boy listening music"
      loading="eager"
    />
      My last projects 
 </div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Demo Project 1"
    img="/post_img.webp"
    desc="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua."
